 \displaystyle\frac{(c-a-b)_{n-r}}{(n-r)!} =  \frac{(c-a-b)_{n} (-n)_{r}}{n!\  (1+a+b-c-n)_{r} } 
\frac{(c-a-b)_{n-r}}{(c-a-b)_n}=\frac{\Gamma(c-a-b+n-r)}{\Gamma(c-a-b+n)}
\Gamma(z)\Gamma(1-z)=\frac{\pi}{\sin\pi z}
(1+a+b-c-n)_r\times\frac{\Gamma(c-a-b+n-r)}{\Gamma(c-a-b+n)}=\frac{\sin\pi(c-a-b+n)}{\sin\pi(c-a-b+n-r)}=(-1)^r.
\frac{(-n)_r(n-r)!}{n!}=(-1)^r,
